# BambooHR
**Category:** ventures
**Domain:** HR software / human resources
**Website:** https://www.bamboohr.com

## Overview
BambooHR is a cloud-based human resources software platform designed primarily for small and medium-sized businesses. It offers tools for hiring, onboarding, time-off tracking, performance management, payroll, and reporting, all in a single integrated system. The platform aims to simplify HR administration by replacing spreadsheets and manual processes with automated workflows and a centralized employee database.  

Since its launch in 2008, BambooHR has grown to serve over 30,000 organizations worldwide, making it one of the most widely adopted HR technology solutions. Its emphasis on user experience and customer support has earned consistent recognition, including multiple top rankings in G2’s HR software category and inclusion in Inc. 5000’s fastest-growing companies list.

## Utah connection
BambooHR is headquartered in Lindon, Utah, approximately 30 miles south of Salt Lake City. It is a cornerstone of Utah’s “Silicon Slopes” tech ecosystem and one of the state’s largest homegrown software companies. The company has played a significant role in anchoring the region’s HR tech cluster, alongside other Utah-based firms like Workfront and Qualtrics. BambooHR actively supports local tech community events and maintains deep ties to Brigham Young University and other Utah universities through internships and hiring.

